CATER, et al.
v.
BARKER. No. 546A05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 10, 2006. Creighton W. Sossomon, Highlands, for Catherine Barker.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 9th day of February 2006 by Plaintiff to Consent to Waive Oral Argument:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference this the 10th day of February 2006."
